 A change of operator or producer, including a change in a
partnership that increases or decreases the number of partners or
changes who are partners;

 Agree to produce the crop as part of a program of crop rotation on
the farm to achieve agronomic and pest and disease management
benefits;

 The payment of such amount does not affect adversely nor defeat the
purpose of the program, as determined by the Deputy Administrator;
